pythran (0.11.0+ds-1) experimental; urgency=medium

  * Team upload.
  * New upstream release.
  * update versioned Build-Depends: python3-beniget (>= 0.4.0~),
    python3-gast (>= 0.5.0~), python3-ply (>= 0.34~)
